## ▶️ How to Run

Run the application using:

```bash
python main.py
```

---

## 🔍 How It Works

* Uses **Psutil** to fetch network I/O statistics
* Calculates sent + received bytes in real time
* Uses **Socket** to check internet connectivity
* Displays live usage and IP address
* Triggers alert when usage exceeds limit

